Ferrari is also the most successful F1 engine manufacturer, with {{sum|{{f1cstat|FER|wins}}|1}} wins<!-- This count was 243 for 1950–2022. --> (having achieved a single non-Ferrari victory with [[Scuderia Toro Rosso]] at the [[2008 Italian Grand Prix]], as well as one Ferrari privateer win at the [[1961 French Grand Prix]]).

